target_resource_location.Description: The location of the target pluginsdk. Required when using subscription, resource group scope or multiple scopes.

target_resource_type.Description: The resource type (e.g. Microsoft.Compute/virtualMachines) of the target pluginsdk. Required when using subscription, resource group scope or multiple scopes.

alias.Description: The Alias Name of the subscription. If omitted a new UUID will be generated for this property.

subscription_name.Description: The Display Name for the Subscription.

tenant_id.Description: The Tenant ID to which the subscription belongs

workload.Description: The workload type for the Subscription. Possible values are `Production` (default) and `DevTest`.

preferred_app_group_type.Description: Preferred App Group type to display
